messages.content:
Certainly! Below is a simple HTML file that includes embedded CSS and JavaScript. This web app allows users to select a date using a calendar picker and retrieves a list of famous people born on that date. For demonstration purposes, I've included a small sample of famous people and their birthdates.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Famous Birthdays</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }
        input[type="date"] {
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        button {
            padding: 10px 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        #results {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Find Famous Birthdays</h1>
    <label for="birthdate">Select a date:</label>
    <input type="date" id="birthdate">
    <button onclick="getFamousBirthdays()">Get Famous Birthdays</button>

    <div id="results"></div>

    <script>
        const famousPeople = {
            "01-01": ["J. D. Salinger", "Paul Revere", "Betsy Ross"],
            "02-02": ["James Joyce", "Charles Lindbergh", "Shakira"],
            "03-03": ["Alexander Graham Bell", "Jessica Biel", "Ron Howard"],
            "04-04": ["Maya Angelou", "Robert Downey Jr.", "Sarah Gadon"],
            "05-05": ["Karl Marx", "Adele", "Bing Crosby"],
            "06-06": ["John McCain", "Natalie Portman", "Steve Wozniak"],
            "07-07": ["Gustav Klimt", "Ringo Starr", "Mikhail Baryshnikov"],
            "08-08": ["Meghan Markle", "Louis Armstrong", "Dustin Hoffman"],
            "09-09": ["Michael Keaton", "Hugh Grant", "Adam Sandler"],
            "10-10": ["Bobby Knight", "David Lee Roth", "Mario Vargas Llosa"],
            "11-11": ["Anne Sexton", "Leonardo DiCaprio", "Demi Moore"],
            "12-12": ["Frank Sinatra", "Diane Wiest", "Brigitte Bardot"]
        };

        function getFamousBirthdays() {
            const dateInput = document.getElementById('birthdate').value;
            if (!dateInput) {
                alert("Please select a date.");
                return;
            }

            const dateParts = dateInput.split('-');
            const monthDay = dateParts[1] + '-' + dateParts[2]; // Format as MM-DD
            const resultsDiv = document.getElementById('results');
            resultsDiv.innerHTML = ''; // Clear previous results

            if (famousPeople[monthDay]) {
                resultsDiv.innerHTML = `<h2>Famous People Born on ${dateInput}:</h2><ul>`;
                famousPeople[monthDay].forEach(person => {
                    resultsDiv.innerHTML += `<li>${person}</li>`;
                });
                resultsDiv.innerHTML += '</ul>';
            } else {
                resultsDiv.innerHTML = `<h2>No famous people found for this date.</h2>`;
            }
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
```

### How to Use:
1. Copy the code above into a text editor.
2. Save the file with a `.html` extension (e.g., `famous_birthdays.html`).
3. Open the file in a web browser.
4. Use the calendar picker to select a date and click the "Get Famous Birthdays" button to see the list of famous people born on that date.

### Note:
The list of famous people is limited for demonstration purposes. You can expand the `famousPeople` object with more dates and names as needed.
